<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #007AFF;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #007AFF;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background-color: #007AFF;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #0051D5;
    }
    .footer {
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .warning {
      background-color: #FFF3CD;
      border-left: 4px solid #FFC107;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>üîî Remindly</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <h2>Sign in to Remindly</h2>
    
    <p>Hello!</p>
    
    <p>Click the button below to sign in to your Remindly account:</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= @magic_link.html_safe %>" class="button">Sign In to Remindly</a>
    </div>
    
    <p>This link will expire in 30 minutes for security reasons.</p>
    
    <div class="warning">
      <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice:</strong> If you didn't request this email, you can safely ignore it. No action is needed.
    </div>
    
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
      If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
      <code style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 5px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;"><%= @magic_link.html_safe %></code>
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>
      This email was sent by Remindly<br>
      Your Personal Reminder Assistant
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
